OL,6,FLegislation aimed at quashing the
OL,7,Fwrongful convictions of subpostmasters
OL,8,Fcaught up in the Horizon IT scandal is
OL,9,Fto be extended to Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FThe blanket exoneration will
OL,12,Fautomatically quash the convictions
OL,13,Fbrought about by the scandal,
OL,14,Fincluding .
OL,16,FMore than 900 were wrongly convicted
OL,17,Facross the UK and the government has
OL,18,Fpaid out almost #200million in
OL,19,Fcompensation to victims.
