OL,6,FPressure had been mounting on the
OL,7,Fgovernment to act on the injustice in
OL,8,Flight of the ITV drama .
OL,10,FWhen the legislation was first
OL,11,Fannounced there was uncertainty as to
OL,12,Fif it would apply in Northern Ireland
OL,13,Fwith Stormont ministers calling on the
OL,14,FLondon administration to act.
OL,16,FThe first minister, deputy first
OL,17,Fminister and justice minister welcomed
OL,18,Fthe moved, announced on Monday.
