OL,6,FPostal Affairs Minister Kevin
OL,7,FHollinrake said: "We always carefully
OL,8,Fconsider the territorial extent of
OL,9,Feach piece of legislation and are
OL,10,Frigorous in our commitment to
OL,11,Fdevolution.J"However, it has become
OL,12,Fapparent that the Northern Ireland
OL,13,FExecutive does not have the ability to
OL,14,Frapidly address the 26 convictions
OL,15,Fknown to be within its purview.J"It
OL,16,Fhas become clear that postmasters in
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland could have their
OL,18,Fconvictions quashed significantly
OL,19,Flater than those who were convicted in
OL,20,FEngland and Wales, which would be
OL,21,Funacceptable."JFirst Minister Michelle
OL,22,FO'Neill said the move was "the fastest
OL,23,Fand fairest solution for all".
